{"tid":1409772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(超重要)高層想出絕招，發夢者必聽","createTime":"2019-08-04T23:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T00:02:49.000Z","uid":140899,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e88b9b56e4819c77cea8c371c5e503a993fea85a","tid":1409772,"uid":140899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:47:19.000Z","msg":"有評論員有以下評論，跪求大家用少少時間由 0:28 開始聽下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H6xREcSfk_Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH6xREcSfk_Q&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=92a4ce25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H6xREcSfk_Q</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然無得Fact check，但由今天起發夢時一定要保持警覺：<br />\n(1) 無時無刻留意身邊有無可疑人物<br />\n(2) 要更小心保護自身安全<br />\n(3) 要避嫌，為免俾人屈，唔好同警對峙，遠離佢地。佢地一來就即走，同佢地保持極大的距離<br />\n(4) 站得較遠的發夢人士可以的話，影低整個事件的發生經過，要影低隻／堆鬼<br />\n<br />\n希望不是真消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184c92e3684e61ed55dc48189d9f27e913d62f74","tid":1409772,"uid":181102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b95a138c4bd183b1257069c7bf2e9181158211","tid":1409772,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:54:35.000Z","msg":"所以大家不要起火"},{"pid":"1dc6bfa5c50c8110e5ecb6de990cb15ad7722605","tid":1409772,"uid":140899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:02:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}